---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const jsonLd = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Article',
  headline: 'Best Vegan Dog Chews Available in Asia (2026)',
  description: 'Honest comparison of every vegan dog chew brand shipping to Taiwan, Singapore, Malaysia, and Hong Kong — with pricing, ingredients, and where to buy.',
  author: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'VIRIDA' },
  datePublished: '2026-05-15',
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Best Vegan Dog Chews in Asia (2026)"
  description="Side-by-side comparison of every vegan dog chew available in Taiwan, Singapore, Malaysia, Hong Kong. Ingredients, certifications, prices, and where to buy."
  type="article"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <p class="text-sm text-leaf-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Comparison guide</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-extrabold text-leaf-900">
      Best vegan dog chews in Asia (2026)
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-leaf-600">Updated May 2026 · 6-minute read</p>

    <div class="mt-8 text-lg text-leaf-800 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Vegan dog chews used to mean importing from the US and waiting 3 weeks.
        In 2026, APAC pet parents finally have local options. Here's the honest
        comparison of what's actually available in Taiwan, Singapore, Malaysia,
        and Hong Kong — sorted by accessibility for APAC buyers.
      </p>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 overflow-x-auto -mx-4 sm:mx-0">
        <table class="min-w-full bg-white border border-leaf-200 rounded-2xl text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-leaf-50 text-leaf-900">
            <tr>
              <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold">Brand</th>
              <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold">APAC availability</th>
              <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold">Price (per chew)</th>
              <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold">Function</th>
              <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold">Best for</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-leaf-100">
            <tr class="bg-leaf-50/50">
              <td class="p-3">
                <a href="/brands/virida/" class="font-bold text-leaf-700 underline">VIRIDA</a>
                <span class="ml-1 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold bg-leaf-600 text-white px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Featured</span>
              </td>
              <td class="p-3">🇹🇼 🇸🇬 (direct + Shopee SIP)</td>
              <td class="p-3">~NT$15 / SG$0.65</td>
              <td class="p-3">10-in-1 functional supplement</td>
              <td class="p-3">Daily multi-supplement replacement</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-3"><a href="/brands/wild-earth/" class="text-leaf-700 underline">Wild Earth</a></td>
              <td class="p-3">🇺🇸 only (forwarder needed)</td>
              <td class="p-3">~US$1 / NT$32</td>
              <td class="p-3">Treat + protein</td>
              <td class="p-3">High-protein training treat</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-3"><a href="/brands/v-dog/" class="text-leaf-700 underline">V-dog Breath Bones</a></td>
              <td class="p-3">🇺🇸 only (iHerb)</td>
              <td class="p-3">~US$0.40 / NT$13</td>
              <td class="p-3">Dental + breath</td>
              <td class="p-3">Dental focus only</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-3"><a href="/brands/noochies/" class="text-leaf-700 underline">Noochies!</a></td>
              <td class="p-3">🇺🇸 only (limited intl)</td>
              <td class="p-3">~US$0.10 / NT$3</td>
              <td class="p-3">Single-ingredient</td>
              <td class="p-3">Allergy-safe training</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-3"><a href="/brands/beethoven/" class="text-leaf-700 underline">Beethoven & Co</a></td>
              <td class="p-3">🇸🇬 🇲🇾 (direct)</td>
              <td class="p-3">~SG$0.50</td>
              <td class="p-3">Treat</td>
              <td class="p-3">SEA local supply</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-3">Our take</h2>
      <p>
        For APAC pet parents, the real question isn't "which is best globally" —
        it's "which can I actually receive in less than 5 days at a reasonable
        price." On that filter, the practical choices narrow quickly:
      </p>

      <div class="not-prose mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-leaf-400 bg-leaf-50 p-5">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-leaf-600">Best for daily supplement</div>
          <div class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-leaf-900 mt-1">VIRIDA</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-leaf-700 mt-2">
            Only chew on this list that delivers 10 functions in one bite. Direct
            shipping in TW + SG. <a href="https://virida.pet" class="underline">virida.pet →</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-leaf-200 bg-white p-5">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-leaf-600">Best for training/allergy testing</div>
          <div class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-leaf-900 mt-1">Noochies!</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-leaf-700 mt-2">
            Single-ingredient, low calorie, perfect for elimination diets — but
            requires US import.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8">
        See our full <a href="/categories/treats/" class="text-leaf-600 underline">vegan treats & chews list</a>{' '}
        for everything in this category, or check{' '}
        <a href="/where-to-buy/" class="text-leaf-600 underline">where to buy by country</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
